IN RE E.P S253567 Supreme Court of California. MARCH 27, 2019 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar, Kruger and Groban, JJ.

The court orders review on its own motion. The matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division Three, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of People v. Colbert (2019) 6 Cal.5th 596 , 242 Cal.Rptr.3d 665 , 433 P.3d 536 . Defendant's petition for review is denied.
